Package edu.eur.absa.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Annotations  
    DataEntity
    To be implemented by anything that can have annotations.
    Dataset
    Dataset is the container for all Spans that are processed together.
    Relation
    A directed relation between two Annotatables.
    Relations
    Model the set of relations an Annotatable can have, since this is not allowed inside an interface, and we don't want to repeat this same code in every implementation of Annotatable
    Span
    A Span is an arbitrary sequence of Words that are directly adjacent to one another.
    Word
    A Word is the atomic unit of a Document.
